} ({in case of} 17... Bb6 $6 18. Rd3 $1 {white is already slightly better} Ne8
(18... Nb7 19. Bg5 $16) 19. Nxe5 $1 Bxf2+ 20. Kxf2 Qc5+ 21. Be3 Qxe5 22. Bd4
