Nh4 $1 {exploiting the weakness of the f5-square.} d5 {the principled move} (
18... Bf8 19. Nhf5 Be6 20. Qf3 Nh7 {Nijboer,F (2583)-Scholl,E (2272) Wolvega
2010} 21. Rd1 $14) (18... Nb6 $6 19. a5 (19. Qf3 $5 $16) 19... Na4 20. Nhf5 Nc5
